<section xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>Vision statement</title>
    <para>
        The project aims to provide its customers a unified vending platform for any tickets 
        (<abbrev>e.g.</abbrev> theatre, movie, bus, flight, ...). The system should be accessible through a wide
        range of access channels, should be very intuitive and easy to use and should very scalable, reliable and maintainable.
    </para>
